## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d7b75-138">下列範例會初始化的新執行個體<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder>類別，並將其加入文字，後面接著的音訊檔案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d7b75-138">The following example initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> class and then adds text to it, followed by an audio file.</span></span>  

